<div id="review_143665085" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/143665085" />
    <a title="Jess" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/4412576-jess"><img alt="Jess" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1438600946p2/4412576.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/143665085?book_show_action=true">Jan 25, 2011</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Jess" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Jess" href="/user/show/4412576-jess">Jess</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>


          <div><span class="uitext greyText">Recommends it for: </span>
           <span class="uitext reviewText">Vampier lovers, young adults, and teens</span></div>

        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer143665085" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16755409378969295533">I was kind of disappointed. I thought there was going to be more to the story. To me, it felt like it just ended. I mean overall the story is amazing but I just didn&apos;t click with the ending.<br/><br/>I like how they didn&apos;t consider themselves &quot;vampires.&quot; That alone brought my attention into the story and made me look at a novel like this in a different perspective. I love the terminology and the story behind to support the terms.<br/><br/>It was a good read. Easy and enjoyable. I could have finished it in one sitti</span>
  <span id="freeText16755409378969295533" style="display:none">I was kind of disappointed. I thought there was going to be more to the story. To me, it felt like it just ended. I mean overall the story is amazing but I just didn't click with the ending.<br /><br />I like how they didn't consider themselves "vampires." That alone brought my attention into the story and made me look at a novel like this in a different perspective. I love the terminology and the story behind to support the terms.<br /><br />It was a good read. Easy and enjoyable. I could have finished it in one sitting. Though I am a fast reader. It was rather nice. Nothing too elaborate and nothing too dull. It was almost the perfect book for me. <br /><br />The emotions do play with you for a bit. I had some parts of me feel bad for certain characters and other times not so much. <br /><br />Again, very good book and was happy to read it. I probably will read it again. <br /></span>
  <a data-text-id="16755409378969295533" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


